WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.360
The right hand in the left hand.

2
00:00:02.520 --> 00:00:05.980
And you're going to place it like a sword there, in the belly.

3
00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:07.300
Like this, here, there, exactly.

4
00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:09.320
To have control here over the hara.

5
00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:12.580
And you're going to start by breathing into your belly.

6
00:00:13.160 --> 00:01:02.151
So I'm going to take a breath, I'm going to exhale through my mouth, like this. I hold my breath for 10 seconds, on the exhale. And then, I inhale like that. Now, you need to practice this exercise 3 times, 30 times. You'll have to increase it over time. You can go up to one to two minutes without breathing.